    "long_instructions": "**Add your landmarks.**\r\n- Add your 2 landmarks to your project \r\n- Set the location and size of each landmark on your map \r\n- Use your arrow keys to make the tour guide visit each landmark\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
